					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Damn. The first test got me good, and made me upvote instantly. Although I have one criticism:</p> <blockquote> <p>This all culminated on 15th June 2005 when [DATA EXPUNGED]</p> </blockquote> <p>I find this sloppy and unnecessary use of [DATA EXPUNGED] because it is very obvious what happened. It makes me feel like you worried mentioning suicide would come off as distasteful when it fits appropriately.</p> 
				 	]]>
